  <description type="morphology">Herbs, loosely matted, 0.2–0.5 × 1–4 dm. Leaf blades oblanceolate to elliptic, 0.2–0.4 × 0.07–0.15 cm, reddish- or brownish-white-tomentose, margins often revolute. Scapes 0.5–3 cm, tomentose. Involucres 1.5–2 mm, glabrous or tomentose. Flowers (1.5–)2–2.5 mm. Achenes 1.8–2 mm.</description>
